{"tid":1660414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳彥霖母:信女兒是自殺 冀事件盡快平息","createTime":"2019-10-17T13:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T14:12:58.000Z","uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da1f4697f7f1c71ed0b06c8192a420931238d1e8","tid":1660414,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:17:43.000Z","msg":"佢阿媽出嚟講...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳知專設計學院15歲學生陳彥霖浮屍油塘案連日引起爭議，外界不斷質疑其死因有可疑。陳彥霖母親何女士接受電視訪問時表示，相信其女兒彥霖是自殺，希望謠言盡快停止，還她及死去女兒一個寧靜。<br />\n何女士指出，她一直與警方跟進，看過所有閉路電視片段，當時閉路電視片段看到彥霖的神情是有異樣的。而彥霖自8月起至少兩次稱，有一把聲音經常在耳邊出現，懷疑她受思覺失調困擾。<br />\n她續稱，彥霖8月到塘福懲教所探完男朋友後情緒失控，其後拒絕付的士車費，並踢到場處理的女警，因而被判入女童院，亦不認同彥霖的死和參...<a href=\"https://headline.klwpc.com/share.php?a=headlinewwd&amp;id=116482\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadline.klwpc.com%2Fshare.php%3Fa%3Dheadlinewwd%26id%3D116482&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAfGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=3a3c45d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headline.klwpc.com/share.php?a=headlinewwd&amp;id=116482</a>"},{"pid":"63fae4230a53da1fc3f0143a5c5eae17e50d4b04","tid":1660414,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dC4rszp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdC4rszp.jpg&h=a54a4986&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a3a40e10c3c6015e171c7823a1779f60a3692ebc","tid":1660414,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:20:30.000Z","msg":"老老實實，究竟係咪佢殺個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好快差佬會捉佢<br />\n<br />\n【行動】西九遊行<span style=\"color: red;\">要大量針對強國人文宣</span>！<br />\n務求<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">輸出革命</span></strong>！附詳盡策略：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659090</a>"},{"pid":"665b0decb7d1431d3d38c2b8442777582c65bbea","tid":1660414,"uid":25201